##=========================================================
## Python data generator
##---------------------------------------------------------
## specgen.py:         generate spec.arff(data description)
## python specgen.py $na $nc $span $cmpr $dist
## parameters: number of attributes, number of classes,
##             stretch means, compress standard deviation
##             normal/uniform distribution for means
## output: spec.arff, head.arff                                                 
##---------------------------------------------------------
## datagen.py:         generate data according to spec.arff
## python datagen.py $N $spec
## parameters: number of data points,
##             filepath to spec.arff
## output: data.arff                                                 
##---------------------------------------------------------
